    &lt;p&gt;Made by &lt;a href=&quot;http://twitter.com/cbracco&quot;&gt;@cbracco&lt;/a&gt;. Code on &lt;a href=&quot;http://github.com/cbracco/html5-test-page&quot;&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/footer&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;container&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;col&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;shortcodes&quot;&gt;Shortcodes &lt;a class=&quot;anchor-link&quot; href=&quot;#shortcodes&quot;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;container-and-columns&quot;&gt;Container and columns &lt;a class=&quot;anchor-link&quot; href=&quot;#container-and-columns&quot;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use container and column shortcodes inside template files like below.&lt;br&gt;
Note the content has to be inline with the tags or 11ty may render it a code block.  It’s just a weird rendering bug.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;language-html&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;  {% container %}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;    {% column %}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;    Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;    {% endcolumn %}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;    {% column %}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;    Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;    {% endcolumn %}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;  {% endcontainer %}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;buttons&quot;&gt;Buttons &lt;a class=&quot;anchor-link&quot; href=&quot;#buttons&quot;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Render buttons inside template files using the shortode below.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;{% button text, href, classes, target %}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;a class=&quot;btn primary&quot; href=&quot;/contact&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot;&gt;
this button was made using a shortcode
&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;language-html&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;{% button &#39;this button was made using a shortcode&#39;, &#39;/contact&#39; %}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;images&quot;&gt;Images &lt;a class=&quot;anchor-link&quot; href=&quot;#images&quot;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Responsive images are generated responsively using either front matter data or as a shrotcode.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Copy an image to &lt;code&gt;/src/assets/images/&lt;/code&gt; and follow the code below.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Caveat: this shortcode does not render when used inside a partial that is included on a page. I know it’s annoying…I’m trying to find a workaround.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;shortcode&quot;&gt;Shortcode &lt;a class=&quot;anchor-link&quot; href=&quot;#shortcode&quot;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;language-html&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;{% image &#39;/assets/images/Pusheen_Zoom_Backgrounds_room_2020.jpg&#39;, &#39;Its Pusheen&#39;, &#39;feature&#39; %}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;front-matter&quot;&gt;Front matter &lt;a class=&quot;anchor-link&quot; href=&quot;#front-matter&quot;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;language-yaml&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-yaml&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token key atrule&quot;&gt;thumbnail&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;token key atrule&quot;&gt;url&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; /assets/images/Pusheen_Zoom_Background_Campfire_2020.jpg&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;token key atrule&quot;&gt;alt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; a pic&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;token key atrule&quot;&gt;classes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token punctuation&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; feature test asodhioas&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;modals&quot;&gt;Modals &lt;a class=&quot;anchor-link&quot; href=&quot;#modals&quot;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An easily customisable modal is included in this boilerplate and can be used as a paired shortcode as below.&lt;br&gt;
Note the indentation of the content with the template tags (again, a rendering issue)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;
{% modal content, modalName, buttonText %}
...content
{% endmodal %}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;language-html&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-html&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;{# start modal markup #}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;{% modal &#39;popup&#39;, &#39;Open Modal&#39; %}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;{% container %}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;  {% column %}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;  this is content generated inside a modal shortcode!&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;  {% endcolumn %}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;  {% column %}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;highlight-line&quot;&gt;  this is content generated inside a modal shortcode!&lt;/span&gt;
